 P_{n+1} \le P_1 P_2 \cdots P_n  + 1 < 2^{2^1} 2 ^{2^2} \cdots 2^{2^n} + 1 = 2^{\left(2^1+2^2+2^3\cdots 2^n\right)} + 1 \\= 2 ^{\left(2^{n+1}-1\right)} +1 = \mu /2 + 1 \le \mu/2+\mu/2 = \mu 
